    <div class="body">
      At this point I'm starting to suffer from BitCoin fatigue. It was funny the first 500 times, but now it's just annoying. If you're stupid enough to hold a cash equivalent essentially in a non FDIC insured brokerage you deserved it. And count yourself lucky and a lesson learned because at least it was fake money made out of thin air and not actual savings. So overall a cheap life lesson.
      
